F. Tam (譚鳴輝), Hanna S. Yuan (袁小琀), Wei-Hau Chang (章為皓), Der-Lii M. Tzou (鄒德里), Rita P.-Y. Chen (陳佩燁), Ming-Jing
Hwang (黃明經).
Place：  Room 114 of the Institute of Biological Chemistry, Academia Sinica
Time：     Thursday,
2:00 ~ 4:50 p.m.
Credit： 3 credits
